original: Lundberg, Sven Gustav Edvard, professor, Göteborg, f. 13/2/00 i Halmstad av insp. Gustav L. o. Maria Andersson. G. 27 m. Linnéa Zell. Barn: Lars f. 31, Karin 35. — Utex. fr. CTI (M). Anst. v. Halmstads Mek. Verk-st. A-B 25-26, Götaverken i Gbg 26-39, tf. prof. v. CTH 37-41, prof. i förbränn :motorteknik där sed. 41.
translated: Lundberg, Sven Gustav Edvard, professor, Gothenburg, born on February 13, 1900 in Halmstad to inspector Gustav L. and Maria Andersson. Married on 27/xx/xx to Linnéa Zell. Children: Lars, born in 1931, and Karin, born in 1935. Graduated from CTI (M). Employed at Halmstads Mek. Verk-st. A-B from 1925 to 1926, Götaverken in Gothenburg from 1926 to 1939, acting professor at CTH from 1937 to 1941, and professor in combustion and engine technology there since 1941.
